{"h42f3e793gb017g4696g908eg0220101692c0": ["We survived - I can't believe we survived!", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "91af9307-7c6b-d379-7af1-3f02f0659d16"], "h8c83a43dg4c13g49edga4e5g9c1856b795d8": ["Erm. Ma'am.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "779d7882-0f8e-dc78-833c-21961117507d"], "h6068a9b1gd00dg43e4g95e3g66248531cbbc": ["Erm. Sir.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "779d7882-0f8e-dc78-833c-21961117507d"], "h3aec94edg4522g4b08g84e6gca067e2cbfac": ["What now?", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "8139cd14-4d69-2dac-daf2-058e795c1e35"], "h10c585c4g1ae7g4d74g9d7cg8b201a818281": ["Find the nearest stronghold and report on your mission.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "b5a7fc84-df96-1cea-0034-22a3f99dd6e4"], "hb580048eg6bdeg4c9eg8033g9b3d525335d5": ["Stronghold. Right. Ed said something about the goblins... Bry will know the way.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "b6c69900-b4df-add5-4712-5b418792ecf8"], "hd9049c2fg0412g4d10g8756g577928d8efe7": ["Thank you, True Soul.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "c4da0e55-9bcf-19af-bfe9-b90b09938c31"], "he81b4734gc916g4e6bgaf90gefc46eec0b72": ["What were you doing before the owlbear attacked?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "be3acd03-e513-3b73-4928-1f305c6f5529"], "h0696ba85g0baeg4fafg996bg7bb320d1d173": ["We were sent to look for fugitives. Some survivors from a crashed ship a ways west along the Chionthar.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "7fae7690-3f31-80c8-35a0-235d3220a661"], "h26d6c2b9g811fg47fdg9b60gf506da2561dc": ["The Absolute wants them found, one way or another.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "932f3cee-d54e-3ca8-04a3-137551bdc9c9"], "h8e2fa76dg6a02g4a57g9869g5907f07baafc": ["It seems you've found your fugitive - me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "4c4f8240-1b58-b527-b9ef-d93a4f7c6ecf"], "hc39da1a2g24c9g4a62gba79g73630d20c3be": ["What? <i>You...?</i> But that means... I have to stop you. For the Absolute!", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "96356273-623e-0892-32cb-e70c1c84f358"], "hb824e3deged29g4ac1ga38cgdb84934e439a": ["Be about your hunt then.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "066e097e-3bbf-9cac-bff1-8717368196f2"], "hd237a162gbdabg40b2g88d7g918316fc938e": ["Right. We will. Bry will know where to look.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "f5113197-df7f-6fb8-f2f0-6a3c4a44b535"], "h936ee4f2g4964g41f9g87d4ga2bed20c3df4": ["Resume your duties in the area - whatever those are.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "48bd631e-ba9f-0a4c-a77c-e9a5d12e4c1c"], "h9bb16c93gf915g4f35gbe93gacd133277b4d": ["It... it got her. It got Bry too.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "43a58d90-e26a-bdb4-0ba2-07c65a213438"], "h210f2452g6d9ag4d7eg8323g18517bff3784": ["Loss is inevitable. You must embrace it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "d1325f83-60e7-fad0-de30-e9f27b4410c4"], "hcb4355b8gde19g4a29g9993geed84d60b083": ["I'm sorry for your loss.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "d1325f83-60e7-fad0-de30-e9f27b4410c4"], "h8cbb35c4ge9c4g48dcga620gcfd2190a96ec": ["What... what do I do now?", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "0140df6e-b73a-7b96-0966-04bde5b6b9f9"], "haf6b6331gb09dg47cag93dcg369ccaece48a": ["Find the nearest stronghold and report on your mission.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "2c99fcb7-483b-5dba-684a-d3702af2f5fc"], "h3c36a5ffgc413g46beg8bfage4828b1d490a": ["Right. All right. I'll go.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "9f5eb51d-3b89-0ef1-8dd9-fd85f022ce22"], "hf910dd93ge9d4g4627gb3b9ga42370a1a745": ["Thanks.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "625d4c86-5182-0fb2-64c3-7c5693495fe9"], "h4bf747eeg28bcg4736g9318g03ca36d145ae": ["Resume your duties in the area - whatever those are.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "bdc763ce-d32f-569d-710d-173b8eb7851b"], "h921c73a4g9d47g4572g9f01g6bc947d8455a": ["This is it. I guess we... go inside?", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "5dca9113-6e7c-f9db-6f03-3cb2201e3e05"], "h48221281ge0e2g4865gb715g87fc00850573": ["How did you get so close to it? What if we're making it angry?", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "ffb05e8b-9393-9f1b-192d-fc53b0c3c911"], "h42e64ebfgb974g487cgb6d8gc3e61950e4b3": ["Just hold steady.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "c3f92202-11b6-4014-edca-546e34a3b0ee"], "hbb06666eg310ag4e9agaf3ag26edf8418edf": ["I'm holding...", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "a1c548fc-45b6-c465-58d9-30ee4241c44f"], "h6c5c8286g6d1cg496aga773g96e50a8edd56": ["You should leave. You'll just get in the way.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "d6944c3b-b8fc-6630-1f25-b3c87f85efc5"], "h3429c184gad3fg496ega1afge461499905b6": ["Of course. If you say so. Erm - where should we go?", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "c1615311-b57d-3600-6178-8744bfe83a5d"], "h1f5fb571gea67g40e1g821fg6001178f02e2": ["Holding steady... holding steady...", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "e8a7f54a-f443-ba58-cd16-31c887085390"], "h9aece5d1g30c2g401bgb644g8b15f15cc176": ["Please. I can't go first. I can't.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "6cad64e6-5913-07f3-a0cc-d9a8073217cd"], "hce4fe0fcg1238g4891gb8b9g0b0d1aceac0d": ["It's just ahead. It's... it's <i>huge.</i>", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "ec2c1087-0b26-23db-5553-e4686a91fbf8"], "hc392d533g4f10g4d56g899eg17ee57d33d8c": ["I'm not sure I can do this. ", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "7c2bf396-9019-0b43-c4bc-1e1b9ed5d83d"], "ha909dd50g66fag4fdfg828agbf60df0dc0ed": ["*The mark glows, but you feel nothing in response. Your illithid power is beyond reach until you rest.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "40f7f48b-eb27-3a0c-8f23-fa51c78773f7"], "h867114a9gd3c9g4878gaafcgc42225fe9bd8": ["This beast killed your brother. Forget fear - where is your rage?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "abd7b7a9-55db-1d47-618f-56d690c9f1b6"], "h35c20a50g7be3g4b1ag9674g3cdde7c1bbbf": ["You're right. We can handle this. And - and we'll do it for Edowin.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "ea6662d3-e538-aa8a-85b0-ca679d1de57c"], "h0d06eda1g2c56g4ab5gac6dg4e75b569c19e": ["The Absolute has plans for you, child - and they only begin here.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "2f4ea23a-4e19-1545-ec1d-edb1b4fbbe03"], "h3ec47adfg0edbg4bd8g9be6g289ac957d1cb": ["Please. I can't. I can't go first.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "78f98be5-508e-87b9-be21-fde3c97b95be"], "h503461cbgc997g4752g80c2gb74630461b3d": ["I just <i>can't.</i>", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "407891fa-1353-b2ae-6f7c-da469322d54c"], "h501889c0gc2b9g43bcg9168g0a3eafc95a9e": ["I have no time for cowards. Attack.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "8c49c6c9-1c9c-bc30-1164-4fa73c0d0e47"], "hfc5b6299g65bbg4bf8g9751g064e5b997a5a": ["Press your advantage now, before the beast smells your fear.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "bc2d0192-bd0a-cd5a-790a-ab3472f13712"], "hef32885eg9835g4cadgb494gbaa7e64e350a": ["Owlbears have vicious tempers - provoke it, and you'll have your opening.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "80f199a7-3653-2b12-6a70-16ff476161d9"], "h4bce84d6g18c8g4e11ga2d6ge57bac89b74a": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "aff3e7aa-b549-a187-5a67-cdf25c71b2a5"], "h278c3ff0g166fg4dc2ga7e1g547a2b12d132": ["*A strange symbol glows, marked on their flesh, and something within you stirs in response.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "c23c71a0-0589-cbff-d770-6e3bf2873998"], "hfe14709ege2f9g4d8dga416g816e9481592e": ["You have no choice. <i>Go.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "f9b883ab-c3db-1e71-ad5f-a419bfc9acbd"], "h6bfb94e7gbb93g4009g9ca2g84302181b516": ["Of course, True Soul.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "6874ae77-c7f7-76fe-ea93-562f8f3bc5c1"], "hc39b3ccbgd212g4663gbfb0g3ece9db54216": ["*A shiver runs across your mind... you feel sated.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "6a7c1a69-ccd8-edf6-a1f6-e65c58490f1a"], "h4eccaf9cga038g4a44g8b66gdb1a383d684d": ["You're right... it's just an animal, and we have the Absolute on our side.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "bfb2d99c-9cc7-161b-cb71-70a66ba1984b"], "h8bd4aab6g338cg4008ga8c1gb814a73b1640": ["For Edowin.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "cb3d213a-f54d-8b9c-d4e0-bb913fa08aad"], "h3b19fbc8g6be9g443fgb565g34be4d89b4f5": ["*Something stirs deep within you, hungry and alert... it's taking something you'll never get back.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "0eaa89dd-d47f-2ac2-0c99-c7cf833522a2"], "hd82926dcg67c9g4dbcga46cga9fe735a0794": ["*Your mind lurches, reeling suddenly as if... bitten.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "4d7b4d5e-4419-c1e1-eacd-555984ac2450"], "hd95ef7c3g41fcg429dgb54dgce4649d17b2d": ["*A shadow swims across your vision, and a familiar voice tells you to be calm. You are loved.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "c176088a-1f7b-ba61-2d17-21b6d93d95d2"], "he3d91dd4g226cg4204g9995gfff166064c66": ["*Your blood runs quicker, feeding the gnawing absence at the centre of your mind.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "cfde004f-72be-feb5-29a2-4208eb85511b"], "h415a3229gbf71g478dgade9g5c4353736dd9": ["*The presence deep in your mind is awake, unblinking. This is it. A single word pervades your consciousness: 'Soon'.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "25ab1f1d-7285-1d09-aab3-1ce452ec7174"], "h2b5ad815g5b42g4604g96c7g14ff5b9a0e53": ["*Your mind is full, bursting with ecstasy and terror. Finally, it is coming. You are becoming.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "b60c75a2-2fd3-83f1-782a-1d5afeb9aad2"], "hc8d636c3gaf1eg4156ga9f8ga2396ea124de": ["Move forward. Your True Soul commands it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "d6a1082d-4e3c-a42f-cd2b-b33846f8d7ee"], "hd14de932g5dceg41cbg8258g200ae2f1b8e3": ["*As the symbol glows, power courses through you. <i>Authority</i>.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist001_InCave.html", "7c484d83-d877-9d36-8794-69abda51f079"]}